isLocked

public boolean isLocked()
Tells whether if this project's element is locked/protected or not. A protected element cannot be removed from the current project.

Returns:
true if it is locked, false otherwise

getWindowData

public WindowData getWindowData()
Get the layout properties (size, position, state of the components) of the window associated with this ProjectDocument. This is used to re-open the window with the same properties it had when it was closed.

Returns:
A WindowData object storing the properties of the window.
